    <item>
      <title>巴里·曼尼洛、布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀等人哀悼克莱夫·戴维斯</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/22/arts/music/clive-davis-death-celebrity-reactions.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，这位音乐高管去世后，斯普林斯汀说道，戴维斯“像对待一个 22 岁的无名小卒一样尊重和友善地对待我，就像我取得了巨大的成功一样。”]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/22/arts/music/clive-davis-death-celebrity-reactions.html</guid>
